00:30:22,080 --> 00:30:23,510
Bem, está anémica.

535
00:30:23,790 --> 00:30:24,880
Anémica?

536
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:27,890
Meu Deus.

537
00:30:30,420 --> 00:30:32,070
Sabes o que fizeste?

538
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:34,850
